that Buddhist texts describe as the diamond body

174
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:42,208
but Jung's concept of self wasn't static

175
00:08:42,416 --> 00:08:45,208
in psychology and alchemy

176
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:48,958
he describes it as a process rather than a fixed entity

177
00:08:49,625 --> 00:08:51,708
the self is not a static entity

