then came the anima or animus

188
00:09:17,416 --> 00:09:20,125
their inner feminine or masculine counterparts

189
00:09:20,541 --> 00:09:21,083
finally

190
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:24,500
they experienced what Jung termed self realization

191
00:09:24,666 --> 00:09:28,000
a state remarkably similar to Buddhist enlightenment

192
00:09:28,708 --> 00:09:31,500
Jung supported his theories with extensive research

193
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:34,916
into mythology religion and alchemy

194
00:09:35,708 --> 00:09:37,000
in his clinical files

195
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,166
