208
00:10:13,625 --> 00:10:14,833
conscious and unconscious

209
00:10:14,833 --> 00:10:16,916
good and evil spirit and matter

210
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:20,000
Jung's late writings reveal

211
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,500
an increasingly nuanced view of the self

