273
00:13:40,541 --> 00:13:42,833
but does not proceed to the next moment

274
00:13:43,458 --> 00:13:45,000
this illustrates how our

275
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,416
apparent continuity of self exists

276
00:13:47,416 --> 00:13:49,916
without requiring a permanent essence

277
00:13:50,708 --> 00:13:52,750
the subtlety of this teaching becomes clear

278
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,500
in the Buddha's careful language

279
00:13:55,333 --> 00:13:58,000
