280
00:13:58,583 --> 00:14:01,666
such a statement would simply replace one fixed view

281
00:14:01,666 --> 00:14:02,750
with another

282
00:14:03,625 --> 00:14:04,625
instead

283
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,875
he demonstrated that what we take to be a self

284
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,208
cannot be found when we look deeply

285
00:14:11,333 --> 00:14:14,000
as recorded in the Samyutta Nikaya

